SIMPLE: ninetieth
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ninetieth
<hw>Nine"ti*eth</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Next
in order after the eighty-ninth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Constituting or being one of ninety equal
parts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ninetieth</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ninetieth
<hw>Nine"ti*eth</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quotient of a
unit divided by ninety; one of ninety equal parts of anything.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The next in order after the eighty-ninth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ninety</ent>⟦br⟧
